{"tid":1848412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ Virus也支化】專家指新型冠狀病毒比沙士「狡猾」","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T16:58:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62082e71b091567b31ce912cdd6eff844bf5a41b","tid":1848412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"國家衛健委高級別專家組成員曾光接受央視專訪時表示，新型冠狀病毒比沙士「狡猾」，原則上所有人都容易感染。<br />\n<br />\n曾光表示，新型冠狀病毒在武漢社區傳播速度快，對病毒仍未完全認識，可能有很多輕症，可能跟一般感冒差不多，形容這場仗在敵我界限不清下展開。<br />\n<br />\n他說，目前是冬季呼吸道高發季節，很難區分感染的是冠狀病毒、流感，或普通感冒，建議將發熱門診搬到公園等公開露天場合，較不容易互相傳染，並將重症病人送到醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505297-20200128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505297-20200128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=e581c050\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505297-20200128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5adbc447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505297-20200128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzVtC0H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzVtC0H.png&h=865c2523&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d69acb5b2a10ff79207286abc26c9d516d7c7ed","tid":1848412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c7fd0c08ee4852102f1b071fa3e3bc640bdbf9","tid":1848412,"uid":392,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28